":"text","text":"1. Design and development planning [820.30(b)]"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Identify and describe the design and development activities and define responsibility for implementation. Update plans as design and development evolve.","marks":[{"type":"italic"}]}]},{"type":"bulletList","content":[{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Design phases and gates"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Resource assignments and responsibilities"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Interfaces between groups (engineering, quality, regulatory, clinical)"}]}]}]},{"type":"pageBreak"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"2. Design inputs [820.30(c)]"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Procedures to ensure that the design requirements relating to a device are appropriate and address the intended use of the device, including the needs of the user and patient. The inputs shall be documented, reviewed and approved by a designated individual(s).","marks":[{"type":"italic"}]}]},{"type":"pageBreak"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"3. Design outputs [820.30(d)]"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Procedures for defining and documenting design output in terms that allow an adequate evaluation of conformance to design input requirements. Identify those design outputs that are essential for the proper functioning of the device.","marks":[{"type":"italic"}]}]},{"type":"pageBreak"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"4. Design review [820.30(e)]"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Procedures for formal documented reviews of the design at appropriate stages of the device''s design development. Each review includes an individual(s) w