   'Specifications for 91-octane and 95-octane unleaded gasoline at retail. Sulphur cap of 10 ppm phased in 2023.',
   '{standards,energy,emissions}'),
  ('SASO 666', 'saso-666',
   'Automotive diesel fuel — Specifications',
   'standard', 'in-force', '2017-09-01', '2017-04-15', '2024-09-05',
   'https://www.saso.gov.sa/en/Laws-And-Regulations/Technical_regulations/Pages/SASO-666.aspx',
   'Specifications for automotive diesel fuel — cetane number, density, sulphur cap (10 ppm for road use 2024), cold-flow properties for KSA climate range.',
